name: "Atom" in the beginning there was HE
description:
"Atom" from -INTERDIMENSIONAL AMBUSH COLLECTION- oil painting on canvas 16x30 shot on polaroid 2x3in by Dr. Andy Milligram (aka Ty'Rone Fisher) this collection of oil painting on film is an experience that conjoins spirituality and man in harmony thru the channeling energy of physical art, by using colors and sounds from a library of synesthetic expression.
in the beginning there was Atom
